    <item>
      <title>奥尔班通过向民族主义者提供银行贷款建立极右翼影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/hungary-s-orban-builds-far-right-influence-with-bank-loans-to-nationalists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙之声党成为最新一个从匈牙利银行获得贷款以资助政治运动的极右翼团体，这是总理维克托·奥尔班在欧洲同胞民族主义者中建立影响力的方式之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/hungary-s-orban-builds-far-right-influence-with-bank-loans-to-nationalists</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:30:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国将实现欧盟 3% 赤字上限的计划推迟至 2029 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/france-delays-plan-to-meet-3-eu-deficit-limit-until-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 将把预算赤字控制在欧盟限额内的目标推迟了两年，以便为修复国家公共财政赢得喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/france-delays-plan-to-meet-3-eu-deficit-limit-until-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰大选前公布免费预算案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ireland-delivers-giveaway-budget-on-corporation-tax-boon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰政府利用跨国公司收入飙升和苹果公司补缴税款带来的财政状况，向选民提供了免费预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ireland-delivers-giveaway-budget-on-corporation-tax-boon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:11:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克什米尔选举结束，莫迪领导的政党面临严峻竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/modi-s-party-faces-tough-contest-as-kashmir-votes-in-final-phase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最北部的查谟和克什米尔地区于周二结束地方选举，人们越来越担心选举结果的不确定性可能会延缓这个动荡省份的经济发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/modi-s-party-faces-tough-contest-as-kashmir-votes-in-final-phase</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 07:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吉米·卡特和他的家乡庆祝前总统诞辰 100 周年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-01/jimmy-carter-and-hometown-of-plains-celebrate-the-39th-president-s-100th-birthday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚特兰大（美联社）——吉米·卡特周二迎来百岁诞辰，这是美国总统首次活满百岁，也是他人生的最新里程碑，他从大萧条时代农民的儿子走进白宫，走向世界，成为诺贝尔和平奖获得者、人道主义者和民主倡导者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-01/jimmy-carter-and-hometown-of-plains-celebrate-the-39th-president-s-100th-birthday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 04:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石破茂出任日本首相 誓言战胜通货紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/japan-s-ishiba-set-to-become-prime-minister-in-parliament-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本新任首相石破茂在担任国家领导人后的首次新闻发布会上承诺将继续努力果断结束通货紧缩，并呼吁日本央行维持宽松政策以支持提振物价和促进增长的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/japan-s-ishiba-set-to-become-prime-minister-in-parliament-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:30:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
